  <description><![CDATA[<p>In an unbeatable ski in, ski out location with five star services and facilities, the TOP Hotel Hochgurgl more than lives up to its name. This luxury hotel has extensive wellness facilities and the piste right on your doorstep.</p>
<h2>Ski in, ski out in Austria's highest resort</h2>
<p>TOP Hotel Hochgurgl has a prime ski in, ski out location just metres from the Groẞe Karbahn lift.</p>
<p>One of the longest slopes in the area runs directly in front of the hotel, so you can easily enjoy the high altitude slopes of <a data-udi="umb://document/6063ab813f384ab795dc6aa1d337f576" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6063ab813f384ab795dc6aa1d337f576}" title="Obergurgl">Obergurgl</a>-<a data-udi="umb://document/5c5a68def0234451a0e7113b85bac993" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5c5a68def0234451a0e7113b85bac993}" title="Hochgurgl">Hochgurgl</a>.</p>
<h2>Heated panoramic pool</h2>
<p>Once you've explored the pistes, you can relax in the 1,100m<sup>2</sup> wellness facilities with its indoor pool and heated outdoor pool with panoramic views.</p>
<p>Try out the indoor whirlpool, steam bath, herbal sauna, Finnish sauna, organic &amp; outdoor sauna and fitness rooms.</p>
<h2>Fondue evening</h2>
<p>Once a week on half board you can enjoy a traditional meat or cheese fondue in the hotel's Murmelstube.</p>
<p>The hotel's two sun terraces are the perfect spot to grab a beer or a hot chocolate and enjoy panoramic views of the slopes after a day of skiing. </p>
<p>TOP Hotel Hochgurgl takes pride in its culinary offering and the menu changes daily offering excellent food in a <span>rustic Tyrolean atmosphere.</span></p>]]></description>
